         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#">
            <p>The council and the people honoured with all the greatest and fairest honours Apollonios 
               Papias, son of Athenagoras, who has been a virtuous man and a lover of the fatherland, 
               and who has distinguished himself in every virtue following the tradition of his family.</p>
         </div>
